# Packet Sniffer (Python)

This project is a simple packet sniffer that captures and analyzes network traffic.

## Features

- Capture network packets
- Identify protocols (TCP, UDP, ICMP)
- Extract source and destination IP
- Extract ports
- Display packet size
- Save packets to log file

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Scapy
- Networking Concepts

## How It Works

Network Traffic
      ↓
Packet Capture
      ↓
Packet Parsing
      ↓
Protocol Detection
      ↓
Information Display
      ↓
Packet Logging

## Run the Program

Install dependency:

pip install scapy

Run:

python main.py